üöÄ DevOps Control Center
Real-Time Infrastructure Monitoring with AWS Integration
üìå Project Overview

DevOps Control Center is a production-style infrastructure monitoring dashboard built using:

Python (Flask)

Docker

Linux System Metrics

AWS CloudWatch

AWS S3

This project monitors:

‚úÖ CPU Usage

‚úÖ Memory Usage

‚úÖ Disk Usage

‚úÖ AWS S3 Bucket Info

‚úÖ CloudWatch Metrics (EC2)

Unlike demo dashboards that show static or fake values, this application fetches live system data and integrates with AWS services to simulate real-world DevOps monitoring workflows.

