Run Container
docker run -p 5000:5000 \
-e AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_key \
-e AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_secret \
-e AWS_DEFAULT_REGION=your_region \
devops-control-center

üö® Errors Faced & How We Fixed Them
‚ùå 1. CPU Showing 0%

Cause: Using incorrect shell parsing.

Fix: Switched to psutil.cpu_percent(interval=1).

‚ùå 2. AWS Credentials Error

Error:

Unable to locate credentials


Fix:

Configured aws configure

Passed environment variables inside Docker

‚ùå 3. Docker Build Failure (pip cache issue)

Fix:

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt

‚ùå 4. S3 Access Denied

Cause: IAM policy missing s3:ListBucket

Fix:
Attached policy:

AmazonS3ReadOnlyAccess

‚ùå 5. CloudWatch Permission Error

Fix:
Attached:

CloudWatchReadOnlyAccess
